title: Index of Rayon Deliveries for United States
notes:
This Series Is Also Given In Rayon Organon In 1940 And 1941. Data Are For Three Month Moving Averages Placed At The Last Month. Data Are Based On Data Of The Textile Economics Bureau, Inc. Source: Federal Reserve Board, Federal Reserve Bulletin, Federal Reserve Index Of Industrial Production, October 1943, And Later Issues.

This NBER data series m01200a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
